summary: A small mod that i made for personal use. This mod offers a small estate in the Rift with its own guards, merchants and cook. There also is a book hinting on future add on, but that may not happen...
descriptionHtml:
*IMPORTANT*
I will no be offering support for this mod because i don't have the drive to continue it, but i will allow people to take over and as long as they credit me :)

Requires all expansions
